---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const email = "kuarahylabs@gmail.com";
---

<Layout
  title="Kuarahy Labs — Solo app studio"
  description="Kuarahy Labs builds focused, privacy-first apps for everyday life — no clutter, no noise, just tools that work. Currently shipping PawRecord, a pet health logbook."
  titleEs="Kuarahy Labs — Estudio de apps en solitario"
  descriptionEs="Kuarahy Labs crea apps enfocadas y respetuosas con tu privacidad para el día a día: sin relleno, sin ruido, solo herramientas que funcionan. Por ahora, PawRecord: una libreta de salud para tu mascota."
>
  <header class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-inner">
      <img
        src="/logo.png"
        alt="Kuarahy Labs logo"
        data-en-label="Kuarahy Labs logo"
        data-es-label="Logotipo de Kuarahy Labs"
        class="hero-logo"
        width="88"
        height="88"
      />
      <p class="brand-mark">Kuarahy Labs</p>
      <h1>
        <span data-lang="en">Small studio. Sun-bright software.</span>
        <span data-lang="es">Estudio pequeño. Software brillante como el sol.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-tagline">
        <span data-lang="en"
          >Building focused, privacy-first apps for everyday life. No
          clutter, no noise — just tools that work.</span
        >
        <span data-lang="es"
          >Creando apps enfocadas y respetuosas con tu privacidad para el
          día a día. Sin relleno, sin ruido: solo herramientas que
          funcionan.</span
        >
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="sunburst" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  </header>

  <section id="apps" class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow reveal">Apps</p>
    <h2 class="reveal">PawRecord</h2>
    <div class="app-card card reveal">
      <img
        src="/pawrecord-icon.svg"
        alt="PawRecord app icon"
        data-en-label="PawRecord app icon"
        data-es-label="Ícono de la app PawRecord"
        class="app-icon"
        width="72"
        height="72"
      />
      <div>
        <h3>
          <span data-lang="en">Your pet's health, in one place</span>
          <span data-lang="es">La salud de tu mascota, en un solo lugar</span>
        </h3>
        <p>
          <span data-lang="en"
            >PawRecord is a simple logbook for your pet's health — vet visits,
            vaccinations, medications, and weight, tracked in one place so
            nothing gets lost between appointments. Coming soon to Google
            Play, with an Apple App Store release planned for late 2026 or
            early 2027.</span
          >
          <span data-lang="es"
            >PawRecord es una libreta simple para la salud de tu mascota:
            visitas al veterinario, vacunas, medicamentos y peso, todo en un
            solo lugar para que no se te pierda nada entre citas.
            Próximamente en Google Play, con lanzamiento en Apple App Store
            previsto para fines de 2026 o principios de 2027.</span
          >
        </p>
        <a
          class="button"
          href="#"
          aria-disabled="true"
          tabindex="-1"
          data-en-label="PawRecord on Google Play — coming soon"
          data-es-label="PawRecord en Google Play, próximamente"
          aria-label="PawRecord on Google Play — coming soon"
        >
          <span data-lang="en">Coming soon to Google Play</span>
          <span data-lang="es">Próximamente en Google Play</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="about" class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow reveal">
      <span data-lang="en">About</span>
      <span data-lang="es">Acerca de</span>
    </p>
    <h2 class="reveal">
      <span data-lang="en">Built by one person, end to end</span>
      <span data-lang="es">Hecho por una sola persona, de principio a fin</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="about-copy reveal">
      <span data-lang="en"
        >Kuarahy Labs is a solo app studio — one developer designing,
        building, and shipping every app from scratch. The name comes from
        "kuarahy," the Guaraní word for sun: small, warm, useful software,
        made with care rather than committee.</span
      >
      <span data-lang="es"
        >Kuarahy Labs es un estudio de una sola persona que diseña,
        construye y publica cada app de principio a fin. El nombre viene de
        "kuarahy", la palabra guaraní para sol: software chico, cálido y
        útil, hecho con cariño y no en comité.</span
      >
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="contact" class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow reveal">
      <span data-lang="en">Contact</span>
      <span data-lang="es">Contacto</span>
    </p>
    <h2 class="reveal">
      <span data-lang="en">Get in touch</span>
      <span data-lang="es">Hablemos</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="reveal">
      <a href={`mailto:${email}`}>{email}</a>
    </p>
  </section>

  <footer class="container">
    <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Kuarahy Labs.</p>
  </footer>

  <style>
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding-block: clamp(3.5rem, 9vw, 6rem) clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-inner {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .hero-logo {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.25rem);
      margin: 0.25rem 0 0.5rem;
    }

    .hero-tagline {
      max-width: 32rem;
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }

    .sunburst {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      width: 140vw;
      aspect-ratio: 1;
      transform: translate(-50%, -55%) rotate(0deg);
      background: conic-gradient(
        from 0deg,
        var(--amber-light) 0deg 8deg,
        transparent 8deg 20deg
      );
      opacity: 0.35;
      z-index: 0;
      mask-image: radial-gradient(circle, black 0%, transparent 60%);
      animation: spin 240s linear infinite;
      transform-origin: center;
    }

    @keyframes spin {
      from {
        transform: translate(-50%, -55%) rotate(0deg);
      }
      to {
        transform: translate(-50%, -55%) rotate(360deg);
      }
    }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      .sunburst {
        animation: none;
      }
    }

    .app-card {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .app-icon {
      border-radius: 18px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .app-card h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    .about-copy {
      max-width: 40rem;
      font-size: 1.0625rem;
    }

    footer {
      padding-block: 2rem 3rem;
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.8125rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 32rem) {
      .app-card {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
